 from the winner in fourth over 1780m at this track. May just need a bit of luck at some point from this difficult draw. Good enough to win a race of this calibre. 2. MY ULTIMATE LOUIE turned in an uncharacteristically poor run most recently when 11 metres away in seventh over 1780m at this track. Form prior to that had been solid. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Leading hope if he is on-song. 3. ALWAYS BE A TORQUE is worth another chance after a last-start ninth over 1660m at Albion Park two weeks ago. 6. DONT FEAR FOR ME last appeared when runner-up over 2040m at this track four-and-a-half months ago. Must be respected.\",\"runners\":[9,2,3,6],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Terry Spargo","tipRunnerNumbers":[9,2,6,4]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[9,2,3,6]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,3,5,7]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[9,4,5,6]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,4,3,5]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,9,2,4]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,8,1,2]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,9,6,5]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"RED","raceType":"H"}},{"